{"type":"message","id":"8322cb8c","parentId":"58890618","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:09:56.100Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户选择了方案 B：全部转为 Cron，删除或注释掉 HEARTBEAT.md 中的重复任务。\n\n我需要：\n1. 帮用户把 HEARTBEAT.md 中的任务转换成 Cron 任务\n2. 修改 HEARTBEAT.md，注释掉或删除已转换的任务\n\n首先，让我创建 Cron 任务。根据之前的查看，HEARTBEAT.md 中有以下任务：\n1. 每日天气推送 - 7:30\n2. 每日新闻与市场早报 - 7:00\n3. 装修任务检查 - 周五 18:00 和周一 08:00\n\nOpenClaw 的 cron 命令格式需要查看。让我尝试创建这些任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来帮你实施方案 B：将所有 HEARTBEAT 任务转换为 Cron 定时任务，并清理 HEARTBEAT.md。\n\n让我先创建这 3 个 Cron 任务："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --name \"每日天气推送\" --schedule \"30 7 * * *\" --timezone \"Asia/Shanghai\" --channel feishu --target \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\" --task \"weather_daily_push\"","timeout":15000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774098582602}}
