{"type":"message","id":"39b69da8","parentId":"1ae9712c","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:16:22.616Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"cron:13","toolName":"cron","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"id\": \"0f91aae7-beb8-4901-bb6e-0a6630d7e169\",\n  \"agentId\": \"main\",\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\",\n  \"name\": \"每日天气推送\",\n  \"enabled\": true,\n  \"createdAtMs\": 1774098982603,\n  \"updatedAtMs\": 1774098982603,\n  \"schedule\": {\n    \"kind\": \"cron\",\n    \"expr\": \"30 7 * * *\",\n    \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n  },\n  \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n  \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n  \"payload\": {\n    \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n    \"message\": \"查询西安今日天气，生成天气简报，通过飞书发送给主人 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e。需要包含：温度、湿度、降水概率、天气状况、穿衣建议。\",\n    \"model\": \"volcengine-plan/kimi-k2.5\",\n    \"thinking\": \"off\",\n    \"timeoutSeconds\": 120\n  },\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"mode\": \"announce\",\n    \"channel\": \"feishu\",\n    \"to\": \"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e\"\n  },\n  \"state\": {\n    \"nextRunAtMs\": 1774135800000\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"id":"0f91aae7-beb8-4901-bb6e-0a6630d7e169","agentId":"main","sessionKey":"agent:main:feishu:direct:ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e","name":"每日天气推送","enabled":true,"createdAtMs":1774098982603,"updatedAtMs":1774098982603,"schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"30 7 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","wakeMode":"now","payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"查询西安今日天气，生成天气简报，通过飞书发送给主人 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e。需要包含：温度、湿度、降水概率、天气状况、穿衣建议。","model":"volcengine-plan/kimi-k2.5","thinking":"off","timeoutSeconds":120},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e"},"state":{"nextRunAtMs":1774135800000}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774098982613}}
{"type":"message","id":"23ddeace","parentId":"39b69da8","timestamp":"2026-03-21T13:17:13.219Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！第一个任务创建成功了！让我继续创建其他任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"第一个任务创建成功！继续创建其他任务："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"cron:14","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"每日新闻与市场早报","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 7 * * *","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行每日新闻与市场早报任务：\n\n1. 伊朗-美国战争最新消息：搜索\"伊朗 美国 战争 最新消息\"、\"霍尔木兹海峡\"、\"伊朗战争 全球经济\"，输出3-5条重要新闻摘要\n\n2. 半导体行业新闻：搜索\"半导体行业新闻\"、\"WiFi芯片\"、\"芯片验证\"、\"ESP32\"、\"乐鑫\"，输出5-8条行业新闻摘要\n\n3. 乐鑫科技(688018)股票分析：获取最新股价、涨跌幅、成交量，搜索公司公告、研报、最新消息，给出持有/卖出的建议\n\n4. 国内新闻TOP10：搜索\"国内新闻\"、\"中国新闻\"，筛选最重要的10条新闻\n\n5. 国际新闻TOP10：搜索\"国际新闻\"、\"世界新闻\"、\"global news\"，筛选最重要的10条新闻\n\n6. 股票推荐TOP10：搜索\"股票推荐\"、\"买入评级\"、\"券商推荐股票\"，推荐10个值得关注的股票及理由\n\n7. 基金推荐TOP10：搜索\"基金推荐\"、\"优质基金\"、\"基金排行\"，推荐10个值得买入的基金及理由\n\n输出要求：\n- 使用飞书卡片格式\n- 每个部分用清晰标题分隔\n- 重要信息加粗\n- 股票/基金推荐包含代码/名称+推荐理由\n- 每条新闻/信息必须附上来源和链接，格式：📰 [新闻标题] - [一句话摘要]\\n🔗 来源：[网站名称] | [链接]\n- 如果某条信息无法找到确切来源，标注\"来源待确认\"\n\n完成后通过飞书发送给主人 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e。","model":"volcengine-plan/kimi-k2.5","thinking":"medium","timeoutSeconds":600},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","enabled":true}}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"cron:15","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"装修任务检查-周五","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 18 * * 5","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行装修任务检查：\n\n1. 读取装修遗留事项清单（在工作区 memory 或指定文件中）\n2. 统计本周完成情况（已完成的打勾，未完成的标记）\n3. 列出未处理事项清单\n4. 生成本周任务完成进度报告\n5. 提醒主人处理未完成的装修事项\n\n输出格式：\n- 使用飞书卡片格式\n- 标题：装修任务周报\n- 统计数字：已完成X项 / 共Y项 (完成率Z%)\n- 分两部分：✅ 已完成事项、⏳ 待处理事项\n\n完成后通过飞书发送给主人 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e。","model":"volcengine-plan/kimi-k2.5","thinking":"off","timeoutSeconds":180},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","enabled":true}}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"cron:16","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"add","job":{"name":"装修任务检查-周一","schedule":{"kind":"cron","expr":"0 8 * * 1","tz":"Asia/Shanghai"},"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"执行装修任务检查（周一版）：\n\n1. 读取装修遗留事项清单\n2. 统计上周完成情况及本周待办\n3. 生成本周装修任务计划\n4. 提醒主人本周需要完成的装修事项\n\n输出格式：\n- 使用飞书卡片格式\n- 标题：本周装修任务计划\n- 列出本周需要完成的3-5项重点任务\n\n完成后通过飞书发送给主人 ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e。","model":"volcengine-plan/kimi-k2.5","thinking":"off","timeoutSeconds":180},"delivery":{"mode":"announce","channel":"feishu","to":"ou_e7a32d874706bf82f2d409b0427b7e9e"},"sessionTarget":"isolated","enabled":true}}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774098982617}}
